{"nbformat":4,"nbformat_minor":0,"metadata":{"colab":{"provenance":[],"authorship_tag":"ABX9TyOWBrT7SihGr7ii7fS98oSr"},"kernelspec":{"name":"python3","display_name":"Python 3"},"language_info":{"name":"python"}},"cells":[{"cell_type":"markdown","source":["### File Handling\n","\n","Python dapat membaca, menulis dan memanipulasi file secara langsung dari program.\n","\n","| Fungsi     | Deskripsi                                                                 |\n","|------------|---------------------------------------------------------------------------|\n","| `open()`   | Membuka file dan mengembalikan objek file. Butuh nama file dan mode.      |\n","| `read()`   | Membaca isi file, bisa seluruhnya (`read()`), per baris (`readline()`), atau semua baris sebagai list (`readlines()`). |\n","| `write()`  | Menulis data ke file. Harus pakai mode tulis (`\"w\"`, `\"a\"`, `\"r+\"`, dll). |\n","| `close()`  | Menutup file untuk membebaskan sumber daya sistem.                        |\n","\n","&nbsp;\n","\n","Contoh kode:\n","\n","```\n","# Membuka file dengan open()\n","file = open({nama_file}, {mode})\n","\n","# Melakukan operasi di file\n","....\n","\n","# Menutup file setelah selesai\n","file.close()\n","```\n","\n","atau\n","\n","```\n","with open({nama_file}, {mode}) as variable:\n","    # operasi file, seperti variable.write() atau variable.read()\n","```\n","\n","&nbsp;\n","\n","Python mendukung berbagai mode saat membuka file, contohnya:\n","\n","\n","| Mode         | Nama        | Penjelasan                                                                                                  |\n","|--------------|-------------|-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------|\n","| `\"r\"`        | Read        | Membaca file, error jika file tidak ada                                                                     |\n","| `\"w\"`        | Write       | Menulis file, menghapus isi lama atau membuat file baru                                                     |\n","| `\"a\"`        | Append      | Menambahkan teks di akhir file, tanpa menghapus isi lama                                                    |\n","| `\"b\"`        | Binary      | Digunakan untuk file biner seperti gambar atau video. Digabung dengan `\"r\"` / `\"w\"` / `\"a\"` (contoh: `\"rb\"`) |\n","| `\"+\"`        | Update      | Membaca dan menulis sekaligus. Digabung dengan `\"r\"` / `\"w\"` / `\"a\"` (contoh: `\"r+\"`, `\"w+\"`, `\"a+\"`)        |"],"metadata":{"id":"OO_RPSOiVt_l"}},{"cell_type":"code","source":["with open('contoh.txt', 'r') as file:\n","    print(file.read())"],"metadata":{"id":"LCruEOirvncG","executionInfo":{"status":"ok","timestamp":1744435025896,"user_tz":-420,"elapsed":8,"user":{"displayName":"Elmo Allistair","userId":"10987414782066235031"}},"colab":{"base_uri":"https://localhost:8080/"},"outputId":"8f137437-7274-459d-b10c-b0309b63d1e4"},"execution_count":6,"outputs":[{"output_type":"stream","name":"stdout","text":["Teks Baris 1\n","Teks Baris 2\n"]}]},{"cell_type":"code","source":[],"metadata":{"id":"la-r5Ln_caK3"},"execution_count":null,"outputs":[]},{"cell_type":"code","source":["with open('contoh_2.txt', 'a') as file:\n","    file.write('\\nTeks baru di baris baru2')"],"metadata":{"id":"yQMyP7e9bly6","executionInfo":{"status":"ok","timestamp":1744435393857,"user_tz":-420,"elapsed":2,"user":{"displayName":"Elmo Allistair","userId":"10987414782066235031"}}},"execution_count":14,"outputs":[]}]}